---
layout: base.njk
title: "Honest Reviews & Buying Guides"
description: "NickPicks publishes independent product reviews and buying guides for home office, luxury beauty, fitness, kitchen, and pet tech. Find the best gear without the guesswork."
permalink: /index.html
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Buy Less. Buy Better.</h1>
  <p>Independent reviews and buying guides — home office, beauty, fitness, kitchen, and pet tech. No fluff, no paid rankings.</p>
  <a href="#latest" class="btn-primary">Browse Reviews</a>
</section>

<section class="section" id="latest">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 class="section-title">Latest Reviews &amp; Guides</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Recently published, thoroughly researched</p>

    <div class="category-filters">
      <a class="cat-badge active" href="{{ '/' | url }}">All</a>
      <a class="cat-badge" href="{{ '/home-office/' | url }}">Home Office</a>
      <a class="cat-badge" href="{{ '/beauty/' | url }}">Beauty</a>
      <a class="cat-badge" href="{{ '/fitness/' | url }}">Fitness</a>
      <a class="cat-badge" href="{{ '/kitchen/' | url }}">Kitchen</a>
      <a class="cat-badge" href="{{ '/pet-tech/' | url }}">Pet Tech</a>
    </div>

    <div class="article-grid">
      {% for article in collections.articlesByDate %}
      <article class="article-card">
        <div class="card-body">
          <span class="card-category">{{ article.data.category | categoryLabel }}</span>
          <a href="{{ article.url | url }}" class="card-title" style="display:block">
            <h3 class="card-title" style="font-size:1.05rem">{{ article.data.title }}</h3>
          </a>
          <p class="card-excerpt">{{ article.data.description | truncate(120) }}</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span>{{ article.date | postDate }}</span>
            <span>·</span>
            <span>{{ article.data.readTime | default("8") }} min read</span>
          </div>
          <a href="{{ article.url | url }}" class="read-more" style="margin-top:0.75rem;display:inline-flex">Read guide →</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="background: var(--color-surface);">
  <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;max-width:600px">
    <h2 class="section-title">Why Trust NickPicks?</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-top:0.5rem">We read hundreds of reviews, compare specs, and cut through marketing copy to tell you which products are actually worth buying — and which ones to skip. Affiliate links help keep the site free; they never influence our rankings.</p>
  </div>
</section>
